SUMMARY:Honey and Cheese Pairing Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Cheesemonger extraordinaire Roxanne O’Brien teams up with varietal honey expert\, Amina Harris\, for an immersive and interactive workshop. Indulge your senses as you experiment with an array of cheeses\, varietal honeys\, and honey fruit spreads alongside an abundant charcuterie spread\, and celebratory mead and honey themed beverages.
