SUMMARY:YOLOFEST: A Weekend To Explore Yolo County
DESCRIPTION:A weekend to savor\, explore\, and celebrate Yolo County\, California\nJoin us as we welcome spring during a weekend-long celebration of everything that makes Yolo County unforgettable March 27-29! \nBest known for its wine country\, Yolo County is also a must-visit destination for farm to table dining\, small town charm\, and of its calming sense of escape from the nearby hustle and bustle of city life. \nExplore farm tours\, ag experiences\, live music\, train rides\, foodie events\, wine tastings\, art exhibits\, special discounts and more during YoloFest! \nVisit the event landing page to find events happening all weekend and lodging specials.
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/yolofest-a-weekend-to-explore-yolo-county/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Wine-Tasting-Winters-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
